in their department.

251
00:16:13,975 --> 00:16:16,562
What Peña's driving at is that
Major Carrillo should man a roadblock.

252
00:16:16,644 --> 00:16:18,397
- We can trust Carrillo.
- I don't have authority

253
00:16:18,480 --> 00:16:20,690
