300
00:18:41,956 --> 00:18:44,125
You should take his phone away.

301
00:18:44,209 --> 00:18:45,460
Five percent.

302
00:18:51,508 --> 00:18:54,093
Suspicious vehicle approaching.

303
00:18:54,177 --> 00:18:57,305
